gencastor (6.0-1) unstable; urgency=low

  * Removed Oracle-specific converters
  * Several minor fixes

 -- Giuseppe Lo Presti <itglp@cern.ch>  Tue, 03 Apr 2007 10:14:57 +0200

gencastor (6.0-0) unstable; urgency=low

  * Port to KDE 3.5.5.
  * Support of signed 64bit int type.
  * Fixed extra ';' to allow compiling with gcc 4.1.
  * Fixed exception handling when committing/rollbacking in Db converters.
  * Disabled generation of Oracle-specific converters.
  * Fixed CVS versioning info in the generated SQL script.

 -- Giuseppe Lo Presti <itglp@cern.ch>  Thu,  8 Feb 2007 17:30:21 +0100

gencastor (5.1-1) unstable; urgency=low

  * Fixed generation of Stream converters for enumerationNoStream stereotype.

 -- Giuseppe Lo Presti <giuseppe.lopresti@cern.ch>  Thu, 21 Sep 2006 09:06:55 +0200

gencastor (5.1-0) unstable; urgency=low

  * Improved exception handling for Oracle converters.
  * Improved generation of classes with custom clone() methods: now is it possible
    to provide a custom implementation in a file called EntityName.cpp_clone
    and it is taken into account when EntityName.cpp is generated.

 -- Giuseppe Lo Presti <giuseppe.lopresti@cern.ch>  Mon,  7 Aug 2006 18:31:26 +0200

