 -- Sebastien Ponce <sebastien.ponce@cern.ch>  Thu, 24 Nov 2005 15:00:00 +0200

gencastor (3.5-0) unstable; urgency=low

  * Improved generation of Objects and Stream converters: a member with
    stereotype 'DoNotStream' or an association to a class with stereotype
    'enumerationNotStream' will not be included in the Stream converter but
    only in the object and database converter.

 -- Sebastien Ponce <sebastien.ponce@cern.ch>  Tue, 25 Oct 2005 15:00:00 +0200

